00:11:46.890 --> 00:11:48.790
Mana mungkin? Kita bersaudara.

00:11:48.990 --> 00:11:50.689
Orang tua kita akan marah andai melihat kita...

00:11:50.760 --> 00:11:52.630
Jangan berani membicarakan Ibu dan Ayah denganku.

00:11:55.229 --> 00:11:57.699
Moo Chi, kumohon.

00:11:58.770 --> 00:12:01.699
Aku berusaha memahaminya

