00:21:31.740 --> 00:21:32.770
Burung?

00:21:33.409 --> 00:21:34.609
Kamu ingin mati?

00:21:34.710 --> 00:21:35.740
Sejak saat itu!

00:21:37.940 --> 00:21:39.550
Maafkan aku. Aku pasti mengejutkanmu.

00:21:39.950 --> 00:21:41.480
Dia masih di rumahku.

00:21:41.550 --> 00:21:43.079
Dia akan segera sembuh.

00:21:43.780 --> 00:21:45.349
Burung yang sangat beruntung.

00:21:45.680 --> 00:21:48.619
Dia pasti sudah mati andai bertemu denganku.

00:21:50.290 --> 00:21:51.359
Astaga.

00:21:51.859 --> 00:21:54.530
Pastor Ko sangat membanggakanmu.

00:21:54.690 --> 00:21:57.030
