00:30:34.710 --> 00:30:37.379
Kamu sungguh berpikir aku menyukaimu?

00:30:38.180 --> 00:30:39.250
Apa?

00:30:41.020 --> 00:30:43.220
Rawat saja burung ini, Bodoh.

00:30:44.589 --> 00:30:47.159
Bong Yi!

